OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShapps: Rail strikes 'could
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe easily settled'         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Transport Secretary Grant Shapps has   
OL,6, said that rail strikes could be "easily
OL,7, settled" by modernising "antiquated"   
OL,8, working practices.                     
OL,10,FHe described calls for him to intervene
OL,11,Fto settle the ongoing dispute between  
OL,12,Fthe RMT transport union and rail       
OL,13,Femployers as a "red herring" and a     
OL,14,F"stunt".                               
OL,16,FOutdated practices "had to end" for a  
OL,17,Fresolution to be possible, he said.    
OL,19,FBut the RMT union said that Mr Shapps  
OL,20,Fwas "talking complete nonsense".       
